rd.com/image/tritip_dwn.gif" width=8 height=7 border=0></a></p><ol><li> <font color="#000000">your name is already taken AND you really, really, <B>really</B>, want that name<BR></font></li><li><font color="#000000"> you only plan on using one ezboard<br /><br />ATTENTION: A Local account will not work on any other ezboard.  You will only be able to log in from this ezboard.</font></li></ol></td></tr><tr><td align=CENTER width="50%"><a href="http://www.ezboard.com/registration/userregistration_global.html"><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/illustra_about.gif" width="162" height="179" border="0" alt="Create a Global Account"><br />Create a Global Account</a></td><td align=CENTER width="50%"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/BBSMessageBoard.showWebRegister?boardName=stormpalaceofbods"><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/illustra_connecting.gif" width="199" height="142" border="0" alt="Create a Local Account"><br /><br /><br />Create a Local Account<br />for stormpalaceofbods</a></td></tr></table></div><br /><br /><hr class="grn" /><hr class="biz" /><div align="left" class="copyright">&copy; Copyright 1999-2003 <a href="http://www.ezboard.com/">ezboard, Inc.</a> All rights reserved. <a href="http://www.ezboard.com/corporate/index.html" class="debold">corporate</a> | <a href="http://www.ezboard.com/corporate/index.html#legal" class="debold">legal</a> | <a href="http://www.ezboard.com/sitemap.html" class="debold">sitemap</a><br /><i>ezboard</i> and <i>helping.people.connect</i> are registered trademarks of ezboard, Inc.</div></div></div><!-- close mainpage area --><!-- checkit ezboard.com version 7.0 brought to you by JR.o guj? --></body></html><!-- registration_choices.html -->

